               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡, Theological Treatise on the Dispute on the Unction (Qǝbǝ‘at) of Jesus Christ; Table blessing, “We beseech you,” ሰአልናከ፡</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="178r" facs="003">Fols 1r–178r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2701Dawit">Psalter</title>
                  <note><ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps118Spiritual"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2000Mazmur#Ps118Spiritual</span></ref>, only for Aleph</note>
                </msItem>

                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                      <locus from="178r" to="183v" facs="180">Fols 178r–183v</locus>
                      <note>excluding <locus target="#181r #181v #182r #182v" facs="183 184 185">fols. 181r, 181v, 182r, 182v</locus></note>
                      <title>Theological Treatise on the Dispute on the Unction (Qǝbǝ‘at) of Jesus Christ</title>
                      <note>incomplete and a sheet (ff. 181/183) has been turned upside down</note>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ነአምነአምን፡(sic) በአብ፡ ከመ፡ ውእቱ፡ ፍጹም፡ በአካሉ፡ ወበገጹ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                      (<locus target="#183v" facs="186">fols. 183v, </locus> last lines)
                      ወነአምን፡ ዓዲ፡ ከመ፡ ተቀብዓ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እምአብ፡ ወእመን[ፈስ፡ ቅ(<locus target="#183r" facs="185">fol. 183r</locus>)]ዱስ፡ በእንተ፡ ከዊኖቱ፡ ሰብአ፡ በእንቲአነ፡ ተሰምየ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ወተቀብዓ፡ ከማነ፡ ከመ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ትስብዕት፡...
                      </incipit>
                    </msItem>

                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="180r" to="184r" facs="182">Fols 180r–184r</locus>
                    <note>excluding ff 181-182</note>
                    <title type="complete" cert="medium" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6205Saalnaka">Saʾalnāka maḥari
                                                  saʾalnāka faṭāri saʾalnāka kahali</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ሰአልናከ፡ መሀረ፡ ሰአልናከ፡ ሰአልናከ፡ ፈጣሪ፡ ሰአልናከ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
