                        <locus target="#181r #181v #182r #182v" facs="183 184 185">Fols. 181r, 181v, 182r, 182v</locus>
                        <desc>are from a rejected leaf of another book with text of an unidentifiable prayer</desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="e1">
                        <locus target="#37r #57r #63r #64r" facs="039 059 065 066">Fols. 37r, 57r, 63r, 64r</locus>
